nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Mr  Person1 I think you may not have gone to the Check Out desk before you left  your last appointment. Going there after each visit is the best way to make sure all get scheduled well in advance. Otherwise the scheduling team does not know you need the appointment. I do have a cancellation for next week if you c an come in on MM/DD/YYYY at 10:00am you can see Dr  Person2 and get your injection. I do see you  have been getting your labs every 8 weeks so there is nothing else you need to do before the appt. I will ask our secretary to schedule but if MM/DD/YYYY is not good for you you can call the office at XXX-XXX-XXXX to reschedule. Thanks Person3 RN
